中教育资源总量；三是多样化发展“提升一批”，支持一批基础较好的地区和学校率先开展特色办学试点，积极发展综合高中，推进职普融通；四是有序增加招生计划“扩容一批”，深入挖掘现有优质普通高中校舍资源潜力，并结合实际优化招生计划安排，有序扩大优质普通高中招生规模。（澎湃新闻）教育部：将有序扩大高中招生规模，解决群众普职分流焦虑问题_教育家_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"CkAI8tuCorDxzf8uEAMaCTEwMDAxODM4MiCr/LqnBjAAOMkDQAFyCTYxOTgyMjkyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"470 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b3b78e598881c757f5fc98065d495d1d_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1693383436.652896","card_id":"Q_619670151","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":619670151,"title":"如何看待华为 Mate60 Pro 没开发布会直接上架官网开卖？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/619670151","type":"question","created":1693288388,"answer_count":61,"follower_count":114,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5263,21576,2628732,2963704],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"这是什么套路？ 我怎么有点司马懿到城下不敢进城的感觉呢？ 外观上重回 Mate40 系列的经典圆环，后盖采用上下分色，两种质感，大圆环套小圆环，正面采用三挖孔镜头。 后置可变光圈主镜头，超广角和长焦微距镜头，5000mAh 电池，88w 有线充电和 50w 无线充电。 售价 6999 元。 哈？"},"attached_info":"Cj4I8tuCorDxzf8uEAMaCDk5OTg0NDUyIMSPtqcGMAA4ckACcgk2MTk2NzAxNTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"240 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-efe314270e9d102fa42757b9d10b622f_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1693383436.653603","card_id":"Q_619680395","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":619680395,"title":"学生趴桌午休 1 学期收费 200 元，东莞市发改局表示「收费合理」，如何看待此事？","url"